Interface SVGMaskElement

All Superinterfaces:
Element, ElementTraversal, EventTarget, Node, NodeSelector, SVGElement, SVGExternalResourcesRequired, SVGLangSpace, SVGStylable, SVGTests
All Known Implementing Classes:
JsSVGMaskElement
public interface SVGMaskElement
extends SVGElement, SVGTests, SVGLangSpace, SVGExternalResourcesRequired, SVGStylable

The SVGMaskElement interface provides access to the properties of <mask> elements, as well as methods to manipulate them.
